#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform.rst:83
msgid ""
"**IDENTITY** = **Transform( 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0 )** --- "
"``Transform`` with no translation, rotation or scaling applied. When "
"applied to other data structures, :ref:`IDENTITY "
"<class_Transform_constant_IDENTITY>` performs no transformation."
msgstr ""
"**IDENTITY** = **Transform( 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0 )** —— "
"未应用平移、旋转或缩放的 ``Transform``。当应用于其他数据结构时，:ref:`IDENTITY "
"<class_Transform_constant_IDENTITY>` 不执行任何变换。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform.rst:85
msgid ""
"**FLIP_X** = **Transform( -1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0 )** --- "
"``Transform`` with mirroring applied perpendicular to the YZ plane."
msgstr ""
"**FLIP_X** = **Transform( -1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0 )** —— "
"垂直于YZ平面进行镜像的 ``Transform``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform.rst:87
msgid ""
"**FLIP_Y** = **Transform( 1, 0, 0, 0, -1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0 )** --- "
"``Transform`` with mirroring applied perpendicular to the XZ plane."
msgstr ""
"**FLIP_Y** = **Transform( 1, 0, 0, 0, -1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0 )** —— "
"垂直于XZ平面进行镜像的 ``Transform``。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform.rst:89
msgid ""
"**FLIP_Z** = **Transform( 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, -1, 0, 0, 0 )** --- "
"``Transform`` with mirroring applied perpendicular to the XY plane."
msgstr ""
"**FLIP_Z** = **Transform( 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, -1, 0, 0, 0 )** —— "
"垂直于XY平面进行镜像的 ``Transform``。"

