#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform.rst:102
msgid ""
"The basis is a matrix containing 3 :ref:`Vector3 <class_Vector3>` as its "
"columns: X axis, Y axis, and Z axis. These vectors can be interpreted as "
"the basis vectors of local coordinate system traveling with the object."
msgstr ""
"基础是一个矩阵，其中包含3个 :ref:`Vector3 <class_Vector3>` "
"作为其列：X轴，Y轴和Z轴。这些向量可以解释为，随对象移动的局部坐标系的基本向量。"

