#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform.rst:187
msgid ""
"Returns a copy of the transform rotated such that its -Z axis points "
"towards the ``target`` position."
msgstr "返回旋转后的变换的副本，使其-Z轴指向 ``target`` 位置。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform.rst:189
msgid ""
"The transform will first be rotated around the given ``up`` vector, and "
"then fully aligned to the target by a further rotation around an axis "
"perpendicular to both the ``target`` and ``up`` vectors."
msgstr "变换将首先围绕给定的 ``up`` 向量旋转，然后通过围绕垂直于 ``target`` 和 ``up`` 两向量的轴，进一步旋转来完全对齐目标。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_transform.rst:191
msgid "Operations take place in global space."
msgstr "操作发生在全局空间。"

